### Drink API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132/api/drink

### Create a new drink
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationId": 1,
  "drinkName": "Coca Cola",
  "drinkDescription": "Classic Coca Cola",
  "drinkPrice": 2.50,
  "imageUrl": "https://picsum.photos/id/163/150/150"
}

### Get all drinks
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get a specific drink by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Update a drink
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationId": 1,
  "drinkName": "Coca Cola Zero",
  "drinkDescription": "Coca Cola Zero Sugar",
  "drinkPrice": 2.75,
  "imageUrl": "https://picsum.photos/id/163/150/150"
}

### Delete a drink
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
